  "description": "A close-up photograph showcases a bouquet of orange and red tulips in various stages of bloom. One tulip is fully open, revealing its dark center and intricate petal arrangement. The petals display a gradient of color, transitioning from a vibrant orange at the tips to a deep red near the base. Several buds are tightly closed, promising future blooms. The tulips are supported by slender green stems and lance-shaped leaves, providing a fresh contrast to the warm tones of the flowers. The background is a soft, muted green and brown, creating a subtle backdrop that emphasizes the tulips' beauty. The lighting appears to be natural and soft, highlighting the textures and colors of the flowers.",
